---
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<section id="contact" class="container-full pb-16 pt-10 md:pb-20 md:pt-12">
  <div
    data-reveal
    class="reveal-sequence panel-dark relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-10 text-center md:px-10 md:py-14"
  >
    <h2 class="relative text-section-title text-white text-balance">
      Find out where your AI investment is losing value.
    </h2>
    <p class="relative mx-auto mt-6 max-w-prose text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-white/90 md:text-base">
      A 30-minute discussion is usually enough to establish whether an independent review would
      produce a useful decision.
    </p>
    <p class="relative mx-auto mt-5 max-w-prose text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-white/80 md:text-base">
      Best suited to UK service businesses with existing AI expenditure, 30–250 employees and a
      specific concern about adoption, cost or measurable value.
    </p>
    <div class="relative mt-8">
      <a
        href={siteConfig.bookingUrl}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn-primary"
      >
        Book a 30-minute discussion
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="relative mt-4 text-[0.9375rem] text-white/90">
      Or email
      <a
        href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}
        class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent focus-visible:outline-offset-2"
        >{siteConfig.email}</a
      >
    </p>
    <p class="relative mx-auto mt-6 max-w-prose text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-white/75 md:text-base">
      No sales deck. No speculative transformation programme. I will establish whether there is a
      sufficiently valuable problem to examine.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
